{"id": 113, "genre": 1000, "title": "你为什么会迟到？", "description": "上班，约朋友，开会，全部都迟到？你并不孤独！FiveThirtyEight最近做了一次调查，参加派对的人到底有多少会迟到……结果表明，准时出席的只有9%，迟到30分钟的占24%，迟到1小时以上的人更多。呵呵，这真是一个随意的世界。\r\n", "record_count": 2675, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183508BJwUQ2hHfT80IluA.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-10-21T08:29:19Z", "questions": [{"id": 106, "title": "你为什么会迟到？", "content": "你为什么会迟到？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 907, "content": "我的闹钟没响", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193623VItfrB8ZnquHmsJ9.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 908, "content": "我按掉闹钟又睡过去了", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193623vSFuRibcHhoWJ79f.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 909, "content": "我的闹钟响了三次被我扔出去了", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193623lU1BQxtyoXOwiePg.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 910, "content": "早晨来得太突然了", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193624p7xna3qMcwg06om2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 911, "content": "公交车一直不来", "image": "img/option/option/201606071936246xL89Hpan3uVNABW.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 912, "content": "我老遇上堵车", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193623VsIcPhS3fkeAnRZX.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 913, "content": "上班来的时候……逆风……", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193630YHmk8rIfM4cWLJpv.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 914, "content": "我有穿衣选择恐惧出门前要换七八次衣服", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193624ai2jyhA0f4Lwc6TV.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 915, "content": "我出门前找手机钱包要一个小时", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193624SKUx35n0DQ1WgEsA.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 916, "content": "我玩着手机就忘记出门了", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193624FG7oi2zRZKtD1m9B.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0},